1
00:00:05,150 --> 00:00:06,605
Who is Bhagavan?

2
00:00:06,645 --> 00:00:09,335
Who possesses all these qualities:

3
00:00:09,440 --> 00:00:12,672
[Who is Krishna?]

4
00:00:12,769 --> 00:00:16,202
wealth, opulences, beauty, knowledge,

5
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:18,577
renunciation, strength, faith —

6
00:00:18,577 --> 00:00:20,236
all of that

7
00:00:20,236 --> 00:00:22,389
to an infinite degree.

8
00:00:22,389 --> 00:00:24,215
And such a person,

9
00:00:24,215 --> 00:00:26,337
if you can find someone

10
00:00:26,337 --> 00:00:31,200
who has all of these qualities to the infinite degree,

11
00:00:31,310 --> 00:00:33,395
such a person would be

12
00:00:34,305 --> 00:00:39,167
irresistibly charming and attractive,

13
00:00:39,275 --> 00:00:43,456
and qualified to be known as ...Krishna!

14
00:00:43,649 --> 00:00:45,345
That is the meaning of Krishna.

